function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	-- Checking to see if this trigger logic has already been activated (just in case)
	-- Trigger volume is actually set to just fire once then delete
	if bCliffTrigger then		
		Hydra.ActorSetNodePath(ID_WHITE_WOLF, tAIPaths[5], Hydra.PATH_FOLLOW_ONE_WAY, false)
		Hydra.QActorFollowPathDynamicSpeed(ID_WHITE_WOLF, tAIPaths[5], "NPC_Run", false)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	--If Wolf never moved to cliff
	if bWarpTrigger == false then
		bWarpTrigger = true
		Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(ID_WOLF_VFX_LOCATION, ID_WHITE_WOLF)
		flVFXTime = Hydra.EffectGroupGetDuration(S_DISSOLVE_OUT)
		flVFXTime = flVFXTime - 0.05
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_WOLF_VFX_LOCATION, S_DISSOLVE_OUT)		
		Hydra.Wait(flVFXTime)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(ID_WHITE_WOLF, true)
		Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(ID_WHITE_WOLF, ID_WOLF_VFX_LOCATION_CLIFFTOP)
		Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(ID_WOLF_VFX_LOCATION_CLIFFTOP, 5)
		eWolf = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_WOLF_VFX_LOCATION_CLIFFTOP, S_WOLF_APPEAR_VFX, true)
		Hydra.Wait(0.1)
		Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(ID_WHITE_WOLF, false)		
	end
	
	-- If player has triggered this
	bCliffTrigger = false


	Hydra.ActorSetNodePath(ID_WHITE_WOLF, tAIPaths[5], Hydra.PATH_FOLLOW_ONE_WAY, false)
	Hydra.QActorFollowPathDynamicSpeed(ID_WHITE_WOLF, tAIPaths[5], "NPC_Run", false)

end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)

	if Hydra.ActorIsInCombat(ID_WHITE_WOLF) then

	-- Checks to see which path node the wolf has stopped at once the player is within range
	else
		if bFirstStop then
			bFirstStop = false
			
			AIPath = tAIPaths[2]
			UF_Move_To_Next_Path()
		end
		
		if bSecondStop then
			bSecondStop = false

			AIPath = tAIPaths[3]
			UF_Move_To_Next_Path()
		end
		
		if bThirdStop then
			bThirdStop = false

			AIPath = tAIPaths[4]
			UF_Move_To_Next_Path()
		end
	end

end

function UF_Move_To_Next_Path()

	Hydra.ActorClearAITether(ID_WHITE_WOLF)
	--This is here in case we set the wolf to a combant at each pause and need it to resume its parth again
	--Hydra.QActorSetTeam(ID_WHITE_WOLF, Hydra.TEAM_NEUTRAL)
	Hydra.ActorSetNodePath(ID_WHITE_WOLF, AIPath, Hydra.PATH_FOLLOW_ONE_WAY, false)
	Hydra.QActorFollowPathDynamicSpeed(ID_WHITE_WOLF, AIPath, "NPC_Run", false)

end
